  "3333390": {
    "name": "Roman Triumph: Survival City Builder Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3333390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/e30f6b984bacbc4f3dcd994665b4eb6e.poster.avif?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/e30f6b984bacbc4f3dcd994665b4eb6e.webm?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/e30f6b984bacbc4f3dcd994665b4eb6e.mp4?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Roman Triumph》是一款背景设定在罗马时代的生存城市建造游戏。你必须领导民众，从头开始建 立定居地，并用城墙、弩炮、弓箭塔和其他防御工事进行强化。面对野蛮人部落，凶猛的九头蛇、牛 头怪、地狱三头犬和其他神话野兽的攻击，你能否生存下来？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/582fa127decdee3ca86fb1c4aec01f19.webp?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/f7e37f1dbcc407416cf88d14334c2ec8.poster.avif?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/f7e37f1dbcc407416cf88d14334c2ec8.webm?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/f7e37f1dbcc407416cf88d14334c2ec8.mp4?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了让城市繁荣昌盛，你必须保证市民衣食无忧、安全、健康和幸福。在这个随机生成的世界中，战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >略性的城市设计将增加帝国吸引新市民的机会，提高资源和食物的生产效率，取悦众神，并在攻击中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最大限度地保障安全。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/5b3fcc5e4ca1359bf976854a099d7778.webp?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/cf45680d32fc370c395db025841ce352.poster.avif?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/cf45680d32fc370c395db025841ce352.webm?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/cf45680d32fc370c395db025841ce352.mp4?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着时间的推移，你的定居点会遭到来自北方日益强大的野蛮人军队的攻击，他们企图入侵和掠夺你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >的土地。更糟糕的是，随着你的发展，你将惊扰到九头蛇、牛头怪等神话生物的栖息地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了生存，你必须建造城墙、塔楼、弩炮和其他类型的防御工事来抵御敌人的攻击。通过在研究树中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >取得进展，你将解锁更强大的防御工事。最后，你可以训练一支军团士兵，主动向敌人发起反击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/47191f1dc7780472083650b20c754cb1.webp?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/bdcb7445d8893d8cb245e93db603ec01.poster.avif?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/bdcb7445d8893d8cb245e93db603ec01.webm?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/bdcb7445d8893d8cb245e93db603ec01.mp4?t=1743445899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罗马人的生活离不开众神。你必须建造神庙，遵守众神的规则，否则众神很快就会心怀敌意，毁坏你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >的庄稼，降下毁灭性的闪电，使民众染上致命疾病，引发可怕的雷暴，或者派遣野兽毁灭你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333390/extras/06eefc0976745ce0beacc661de75b805.webp?t=1743445899\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过种植农作物和饲养动物来管理民众的食物需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集资源来建造更多住房、工业建筑、社会和宗教建筑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过满足民众的需求来保持他们的生产力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过建造神庙和献祭来崇拜神明，以免遭其怒火。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >研究并解锁50多座独特的罗马建筑（客栈、公寓、元老院……）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他城市进行资源贸易。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与九头蛇和牛头怪等罗马神话生物战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造防御工事（弩炮、弓箭手、蝎式弩等）并训练军团士兵来保卫城市</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序生成的逼真景观/地图，包含各种动物和壮丽的自然风光。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
